Where to Get Actual API Keys
If you need real API keys for development/testing, here are some options:

Service	Type	How to Get
Azure Face API	Facial Recognition	Sign up at Azure portal, create Face resource
Amazon Rekognition	Facial Analysis	AWS Console > Rekognition > Get started
Google Cloud Vision	Face Detection	Google Cloud Console > Enable Vision API
Kairos	Face Recognition	kairos.com > Sign up for free tier
Ethereum/Alchemy	Blockchain	alchemy.com > Create app for blockchain logging